CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 17, 1939, pg. 15 reads: "Topnotch Golfers Who Participated In Elk Open Tourney - Despite inclement weather conditions, the Pittsburgh Elks Open Golf tournament was one of the most successful ever held here. Dave Wilson, former Peabody High golf captain, won top honors by carding a brilliant 74 on the difficult South Park 18-hold course...Photo by Harris."
TitMainTitle: Golfer Dave Wilson swinging golf club at South Park golf course during Pittsburgh Elks Open golf tournament
